        <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-10 col-xs-10">
            <p class="lead">When you order myComputer, you receive 24 customized,
            to-the-minute articles or papers in your 3 chosen topics selected
            from 13 leading peer-reviewed magazines and 200 conferences.</p>
            <p class="lead">You can access these important articles - along with
                your monthly digital <i>Computer</i> magazine - via your desktop,
                tablet, or mobile device.</p>
        </div>
